title: Memphis Taproom
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Restaurant, bar, and beer garden. Several menu items are vegetarian and/or vegan. Relaxed and cozy atmosphere. Weekend brunch til 3pm. The kitchen stops serving food at midnight. Note: Reported that they don't have a dedicated veg fryer. Meat is fried in the same oil as anything you might order as "vegan. Please confirm and let HappyCow know.
